title: PTOS-open-data
text:
Welcome
This is a workshop on open data.
If you like the workshop and want to keep it forever, make it yours. You can

fork the github repo this Quarto book is based on
go to settings of you new repo and go to “pages”. Then set … to “gh-pages”
set the description of your repo to …
open your new webpage by clicking on …
